+     * mdpartydll's own ring/swirl backdrop prop. No-op when widescreen is
+     * disabled. */
+    /* Converted from a plain uniform scale to a bbox-center-aware extrude:
+     * this backdrop is 5 sub-objects (day/sky/night panels, a grid layer,
+     * and a light-glow accent), each with real, non-zero base.pos, so
+     * scaling about local origin was scaling about the wrong point for
+     * every one of them -- this helper composes each sub-object's own base
+     * transform first to find the correct composite center. Of this
+     * model's attribute pool, 4 entries are GX_CLAMP and bound to all 5
+     * visible sub-objects' primary texture; one GX_REPEAT entry exists but
+     * isn't bound to any of their primary attributes (purpose unresolved),
